  metaDescription: 'Brisbane is Australia\'s fastest growing capital city. Here is a suburb-by-suburb analysis of the best areas to open a restaurant in 2026.',
  primaryKeyword: 'best areas to open a restaurant in Brisbane',
  secondaryKeywords: ['Brisbane restaurant location', 'West End restaurant Brisbane', 'Fortitude Valley food business', 'Brisbane dining market analysis', 'restaurant location Brisbane 2026'],
